    <section class="words-list-container">
      <header>
        <h1>Words</h1>
        <p>
          I write a lot of different things. From tech howtos to philosophical musings to
          speculative fiction to mundane blog posts about what's going on in my life. Here
          is a collection of works I thought were better shared with you than sitting in a
          box in my closet. Enjoy.
        </p>
